+## Toolchain
+
+The generated service consumes Kernel in two ways:
+
+```text
+build-time tools:
+  go install github.com/aisphereio/kernel/cmd/protoc-gen-go-http@__KERNEL_VERSION__
+  go install github.com/aisphereio/kernel/cmd/protoc-gen-go-errors@__KERNEL_VERSION__
+  go install github.com/aisphereio/kernel/cmd/protoc-gen-go-authz@__KERNEL_VERSION__
+  go install github.com/aisphereio/kernel/cmd/buf-check-aisphere@__KERNEL_VERSION__
+
+runtime package:
+  require github.com/aisphereio/kernel __KERNEL_VERSION__
+```
+
+Install project-local tools into `.bin`:
+
+```bash
+make tools
+```
+
+Windows without GNU make:
+
+```powershell
+powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\scripts\tools.ps1
+```
+
 ## Generate
 
 ```bash
-buf generate --template buf.gen.yaml
+make api
+make proto-check
 ```
 
 ## Verify
